<H3> <TI>   Croatian-Muslim Agreement `Turkish Initiative' </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA0203195894 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1600 
GMT 2 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0203195894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Turkey has stated that the federation agreement 
reached between the Croatians and the Muslims in 
Bosnia-Herzegovina is a significant step taken toward a lasting 
and just solution. 
  Foreign Ministry Deputy Spokesman Ferhat Ataman, at his 
weekly news conference, stated that Turkey undertook intensive 
efforts toward furthering Croatian-Muslim cooperation. Ataman 
further noted that this agreement developed from Turkish 
initiative. 

</TEXT>

