<H3> <TI>   Agreements, Negotiations Reported in EU Expansion Talks </TI></H3>
<H4>   Austria's Mock Announces Agreement </H4>
<F P=102> AU0103213194 Vienna ORF Teletext in German 2114 GMT 1 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU0103213194 </F>
<F P=104>  Vienna ORF Teletext </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> German </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] "The European Union and Austria have agreed on 
membership." This flash report by Austria Press Agency, APA, of 
2110 GMT quotes Foreign Minister Alois Mock. In an 
unprecedented negotiating marathon, the contentious issues -- 
transit traffic and agriculture -- were settled. Details are 
not yet available. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS3-18474 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drweu041cc_94002" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-WEU-94-041 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
