<H3> <TI>   Court Sentences 5 for Sabotaging Fighter Aircraft </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0303233994 Stockholm Radio Sweden in Swedish 1645 GMT 3 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0303233994 </F>
<F P=104>  Stockholm Radio Sweden </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Swedish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Lidkoeping town court today sentenced five 
people who were accused of entering the F-7 Wing in Saatenaes 
and destroying the nose section of a Viggen fighter aircraft. 
The man and the woman who carried out the actual deed were 
sentenced to a year and two months, and three months 
imprisonment, respectively, for gross sabotage, Radio Skaraborg 
reports. Two others involved received sentences of one year 
each for assisting gross sabotage. The fifth accused received a 
suspended sentence. 

</TEXT>

