<F P=100> ANNEX </F>
<F P=101> Italy &amp; Vatican City </F>
<H3> <TI>   Comit's Public Share Offer Successful </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BR0203130594 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1844 GMT 1 
Mar 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

