<F P=100> TURKEY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Government Officials Comment on Deputies' Immunity </TI></H3>
<H4>   Party Leader Criticizes Action </H4>
<F P=102> TA0403201994 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1800 
GMT 4 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0403201994 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


